name: ExtensionTransport
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.Transport` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `Transport` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `Transport` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`Transport` 0..* `Transport`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
* R5 `Transport` 0..* `Transport`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `Transport` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `Transport` is not mapped.

BasedOn refers to a higher-level authorization that triggered the creation of the transport.  It references a "request" resource such as a ServiceRequest or Transport, which is distinct from the "request" resource the Transport is seeking to fulfill.
